document.full_text: pakistan's parliament condemned on saturday the u.s. raid that killed osama bin laden, warning pakistan might cut supply lines to u.s. forces in afghanistan if there were further military incursions.
document.title: pakistan's parliament warns u.s. over bin laden raid
